snippet.title: Alfaim (アルフェイム) for the NEC PC-88
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

---


Game description:

Alfaim is a detective visual novel game.

You play as Ryo Ikeuchi and your best friend Okuuchi Takeshi has apparently committed suicide, but you don't believe that. It is up to you to find the murderer of your best friend.
